Building LEDSpicer

Essential:
	build-essential
	autoconf
	libtool
Libraries:
	libusb-1.0
	tinyxml2

If documentation is needed:
	doxygen
	dot (for diagrams)

Prepare tools:
	./autogen.sh
	./configure
	or
	./configure CXXFLAGS='-g0 -O3'
	For developers (will enable debug g3, disable optimizations and activate the debug level for logs):
	./configure --enable-develop

then compile with:
	make

Install (needs root access):
	make install
